{"tid":970434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我建議獨派可先組織反黑隊","createTime":"2019-01-05T20:21:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T14:01:35.000Z","uid":74214,"like":56,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"653a7d0f20983b37df9a28d1f57b078db1cf843e","tid":970434,"uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T20:21:59.000Z","msg":"全民反黑<br />\n晚晚搞鳩黑社會啲場<br />\n<br />\n學某巴打話齋<br />\n新潮流係警黑合作<br />\n警察唔方便搞政治果邊 黑就負責出手<br />\n由雨傘到宜家獨派俾人搞<br />\n就知道未來趨勢係警黑合作<br />\n注定無運行<br />\n<br />\n既然警個邊 你地郁唔到<br />\n有無打算以牙還牙班黑社會<br />\n話俾佢地知<br />\n搞鳩獨派係有代價嘅<br />\n<br />\n至於點樣搞鳩班黑社會要諗諗<br />\n譬如盡公民責任打電話舉報罪案<br />\n或者好似光復上水咁光復油尖旺？"},{"pid":"b7ae9d61ca19b761d2ca8007c494511395c43b1f","tid":970434,"uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T20:26:40.000Z","msg":"利申鳩upper"},{"pid":"d8b142352feb45576335cc04c7287009eb0ff7b2","tid":970434,"uid":167506,"like":29,"dislike":10,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T20:27:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/03/201047_e4667600800c1e449924e25ec9f739e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F03%2F201047_e4667600800c1e449924e25ec9f739e2.jpg&h=80f7391a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1288869bd7d3b22b0681d29963643c3c8daed920","tid":970434,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T20:30:43.000Z","msg":"驚 +  黑<br />\n<br />\n你玩埋我果份"},{"pid":"5b6adba4e1430d912d7798402b1fdb31b40a3dee","tid":970434,"uid":123264,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T20:31:56.000Z","msg":"弱智<br />\n警察拉你唔拉生菜排骨 咁你點算?"},{"pid":"0c539256c8edac9aa739ef83993a05185ea949c7","tid":970434,"uid":98692,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T20:49:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 警察打人都要行埋角落，黑社會就直接打你。你連7警都打唔贏諗住挑黑社會？"},{"pid":"efbd7e1e5527e4441311842a88dd36b36cf610f1","tid":970434,